sentences: Riki Miura (三浦 力, Miura Riki, born October 17, 1983) is a Japanese actor from Hiroshima Prefecture.
Miura made his acting debut in 2005.
He announced on March 10, 2018 that he will retire from the entertainment business on March 31, 2018.
